{"tid":177644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★香港成為支那一個普通城市，樓價會否大跌？","createTime":"2017-03-29T04:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T06:10:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b6c580b36b469b518c6ceedd5f0346778a449a","tid":177644,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"美國國會及行政當局中國委員會批評，北京明顯干預香港行政長官選舉，再次嚴重削弱香港自治權。  <br />\n<br />\n委員會發表聲明，批評北京官員強調中央有權介入選舉，同時向選委施壓，促使他們投票給候任行政長官林鄭月娥。聲明又關注選舉結束後，「佔領行動」多位領袖隨即被起訴。委員會憂慮林鄭月娥難以應對香港自治和司法日益受損，呼籲她根據港人的民主訴求，推動有意義的政制改革。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">委員會重申一旦香港自由受損，只是另一個中國城市，將重新評估是否繼續根據《香港關係法》，給予香港特別對待。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/58dabeea6db28c92209aceef/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F58dabeea6db28c92209aceef%2F&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fc41f85a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/58dabeea6db28c92209aceef/</a>"},{"pid":"6cb786f0592119a001727e8a279b596ad8908dca","tid":177644,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696c12457855b99d19c244e5347ceafbf89a5281","tid":177644,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"樓價都會變成支那一個普通城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a0d6b6acf17e96fd3d409222a2a17819cc05eb","tid":177644,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"而家大陸樓好平咩？"},{"pid":"f62c6549d0cc03db111f4b8a9b8ce1338fe8c711","tid":177644,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:22:57.0